ds more.\", \"from\": 23697, \"to\": 23774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good work\", \"from\": 23729, \"to\": 23738}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 23754, \"to\": 23762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Ben Henley:We have to deal with climate change and it's the long term driver of the risk to the reef.\", \"from\": 23776, \"to\": 23880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 23811, \"to\": 23825}, {\"ngram\": \"the long term driver\", \"from\": 23835, \"to\": 23855}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 23859, \"to\": 23867}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 23871, \"to\": 23879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elizabeth Cramsie:Dr Lissa Schindler is from the Australian Marine Conservation Society.\", \"from\": 23882, \"to\": 23970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23903, \"end\": 23908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leszno\", \"score\": 0.9999999979962695, \"rank\": 1.401571478547451e-09, \"text\": \"Lissa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leszno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leszno\"}, {\"begin\": 23931, \"end\": 23969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Marine_Conservation_Society\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Marine Conservation Society\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Marine_Conservation_Society\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Marine_Conservation_Society\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Lissa Schindler:It was the highest and most prolonged and extreme temperatures that the Great Barrier Reef has experienced and that's why we saw such huge impact from a bleaching perspective.\", \"from\": 23972, \"to\": 24166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the highest and most prolonged and extreme temperatures\", \"from\": 23998, \"to\": 24053}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Barrier Reef\", \"from\": 24059, \"to\": 24081}, {\"ngram\": \"such huge impact\", \"from\": 24120, \"to\": 24136}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleaching perspective\", \"from\": 24142, \"to\": 24165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elizabeth Cramsie:Alan Wallish says it's not all doom and gloom but ensuring the ongoing health of the reef will take a combined effort.\", \"from\": 24168, \"to\": 24304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alan Wallish\", \"from\": 24186, \"to\": 24198}, {\"ngram\": \"all doom\", \"from\": 24213, \"to\": 24221}, {\"ngram\": \"gloom\", \"from\": 24226, \"to\": 24231}, {\"ngram\": \"the ongoing health\", \"from\": 24245, \"to\": 24263}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 24267, \"to\": 24275}, {\"ngram\": \"a combined effort\", \"from\": 24286, \"to\": 24303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alan Wallish:The Great Barrier Reef is not one thing.\", \"from\": 24306, \"to\": 24359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alan Wallish\", \"from\": 24306, \"to\": 24318}, {\"ngram\": \"The Great Barrier Reef\", \"from\": 24319, \"to\": 24341}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 24349, \"to\": 24358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a huge living organism that's over 2000km long and what happens on one section might not necessarily happen on another.\", \"from\": 24360, \"to\": 24484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge living organism\", \"from\": 24365, \"to\": 24387}, {\"ngram\": \"one section\", \"from\": 24432, \"to\": 24443}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 24476, \"to\": 24483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a little bit of a canary in the coal mine.\", \"from\": 24485, \"to\": 24533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 24491, \"to\": 24503}, {\"ngram\": \"a canary\", \"from\": 24507, \"to\": 24515}, {\"ngram\": \"the coal mine\", \"from\": 24519, \"to\": 24532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we do want to protect our precious resource here and we need to be working together, science, tourism operators, the communities, traditional owners etc.\", \"from\": 24534, \"to\": 24690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our precious resource\", \"from\": 24559, \"to\": 24580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an all encompassing thing that we need to do.\", \"from\": 24691, \"to\": 24744, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an all encompassing thing\", \"from\": 24699, \"to\": 24724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephanie Smail:Great Barrier Reef tour operator Alan Wallish ending that report by Elizabeth Cramsie.\", \"from\": 24746, \"to\": 24848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24746, \"end\": 24755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\", \"score\": 0.9875563425449132, \"rank\": 0.011253201848390477, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Plum\"}, {\"begin\": 24756, \"end\": 24761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"score\": 0.9999992977382327, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smail\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smail\"}, {\"begin\": 24830, \"end\": 24839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9888688434910875, \"rank\": 0.01023332776670064, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Great Barrier Reef tour operator Alan Wallish\", \"from\": 24762, \"to\": 24807}, {\"ngram\": \"that report\", \"from\": 24815, \"to\": 24826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's all from the World Today team.\", \"from\": 24849, \"to\": 24890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Today team\", \"from\": 24869, \"to\": 24889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for your company.\", \"from\": 24891, \"to\": 24915, \"entities\